obj9520@khanjar.desc[0]: A green leather mask is lying here.

obj9510@khanjar.desc[0]: A small talon is lying here.

obj9507_1@khanjar.desc[0]: A brown belt is lying here.

cupboard_khanjar9506@khanjar.name: cupboard_khanjar9506
cupboard_khanjar9506@khanjar.examine:
The cupboard is of some lacquered wood and the handicraft appears
excellent.  The doubledoors of it are covered in a big painted picture,
presenting a march of an ancient fully equipped army.  There are also 
two large handles of pronze, formed in interesting spiral.

obj9514@khanjar.name: obj9514
obj9514@khanjar.desc[0]: A pair of brown leggings is lying here.

door_khanjar9511@khanjar.name: door_khanjar9511
door_khanjar9511@khanjar.examine: You see a room in confusion...

bush_khanjar9522@khanjar.name: bush_khanjar9522
bush_khanjar9522@khanjar.examine:
It appears old and greyish.  It looks as if there were something dark
behind it... perhaps.

door_khanjar9504@khanjar.name: door_khanjar9504
door_khanjar9504@khanjar.examine: You see the yard of the tavern.

obj9508@khanjar.name: obj9508
obj9508@khanjar.desc[0]: A small earring is lying here.

obj9505_1@khanjar.name: obj9505_1
obj9505_1@khanjar.desc[0]: A red-handled knife is lying here.

obj9520_1@khanjar.name: obj9520_1
obj9520_1@khanjar.desc[0]: A green leather mask is lying here.

obj9513@khanjar.name: obj9513
obj9513@khanjar.desc[0]: A conical, peculiar hat is lying here.

obj9502@khanjar.name: obj9502
obj9502@khanjar.desc[0]: A small pendant is lying here.

remnants_khanjar9541@khanjar.name: remnants_khanjar9541
remnants_khanjar9541@khanjar.examine: You see what mainly are small bones.

obj9507@khanjar.name: obj9507
obj9507@khanjar.desc[0]: A brown belt is lying here.

obj9505@khanjar.name: obj9505
obj9505@khanjar.desc[0]: A red-handled knife is lying here.

statue_khanjar9568@khanjar.name: statue_khanjar9568
statue_khanjar9568@khanjar.examine:
The statue is of light wood and appears very skillfully carved.  
The woman it presents has a tall lenght of straight hair almost 
reaching her legs.  Worn on her head is a crown made of the most 
beautiful flowers, barely found in every forest.  Couple of small 
birds are sitting on her shoulders, seemingly listening earnestly.  
This must be the Queen of the Forest herself.

obj9509@khanjar.name: obj9509
obj9509@khanjar.desc[0]: A small pair of mittens is lying here.

obj9509_1@khanjar.name: obj9509_1
obj9509_1@khanjar.desc[0]: A small pair of mittens is lying here.

obj9504@khanjar.desc[0]: A tiny pair of shoes is here.

obj9508_1@khanjar.desc[0]: A small earring is lying here.

obj9512@khanjar.name: obj9512
obj9512@khanjar.desc[0]: A small lantern of wood is lying here.

gate_khanjar9502@khanjar.name: gate_khanjar9502
gate_khanjar9502@khanjar.examine: You see the yard of the tavern.

door_khanjar9502@khanjar.name: door_khanjar9502
door_khanjar9502@khanjar.examine: You see the yard of this tavern.

gate_khanjar9501@khanjar.name: gate_khanjar9501
gate_khanjar9501@khanjar.examine: You see the paved path behind the fence.

obj9511@khanjar.name: obj9511
obj9511@khanjar.desc[0]: A modest green rucksack is lying here.

obj9530@khanjar.desc[0]: A small bronze key is lying here.

obj9501@khanjar.desc[0]: A red ring is lying here.

obj9515@khanjar.name: obj9515
obj9515@khanjar.desc[0]: A tankard of beer is here.

obj9506_1@khanjar.desc[0]: A small jerkin is lying here.

door_khanjar9505@khanjar.examine: You see a small, wooden building.

obj9510_1@khanjar.name: obj9510_1
obj9510_1@khanjar.desc[0]: A small talon is lying here.

door_khanjar9546@khanjar.name: door_khanjar9546
door_khanjar9546@khanjar.examine: You see a dwelling of some kind.

obj9531@khanjar.name: obj9531
obj9531@khanjar.desc[0]: A small iron key is lying here.

khanjar9577@khanjar.title: Climbing the Gorge
khanjar9577@khanjar.description:
Despite all better judgements, you claw your way along the side of the
walls.  Be aware though, one false move and you will fall to your death.

khanjar9566@khanjar.title: Before The Wooden Steps
khanjar9566@khanjar.description:
Just before you lie firm, wooden steps, ascending onto the dias.  
Simple, but elegant symbols have been encarved on them.

khanjar9549@khanjar.title: Before An Ancient Poplar
khanjar9549@khanjar.description:
You are standing at a grove.  Just before you is a large poplar, which 
foliage spreads in every direction like a gigantic green ball.  Its trunk 
is gnarled and carries the scars of hundreds of years.  A small hole appears 
to penetrate into the pith of the tree.

khanjar9514@khanjar.title: At The Forest Edge
khanjar9514@khanjar.description:
You are walking on a brownish path that leads towards a light 
forest to the east, and begins to wriggle its way there.  A mild 
chirping can be heard from somewhere nearby.
   The city of Sundhaven is further away to the west.

khanjar9999@khanjar.title: Falling Down
khanjar9999@khanjar.description:
Whoops...you slip, you fall, you DIE!!!  Don't feel bad, you aren't the
only one who hasn't mastered climbing the side of a gorge.

khanjar9538@khanjar.title: A Small Brook
khanjar9538@khanjar.description:
This small brook streams somewhere from the highest summits of the 
mountain.  Its water is clear and very refreshive, and you can see the
sunshine make it sparkle splendid at the upper course of the brook where
lies a picturesque waterfall.  A small bridge allows passage.

khanjar9546@khanjar.title: An Underground Dwelling
khanjar9546@khanjar.description:
The space is a small, round chamber, lit by an extraordinary 
chandelier made of the rhizome of a tree standing above there.  All around 
lie small pieces of furniture, most of which you probably could not use, 
for they are rather tiny.  However, they are skillfully constructed,
revealing both the artistic and practical abilities of whoever was the
maker.  A thick, multicolorous carpet covers the floor.
   To the west is a small, wooden door.

khanjar9558@khanjar.title: On A Grey Trunk
khanjar9558@khanjar.description:
Reaching the foot of the hillside you notice a large greyish trunk, 
penetrating into the forest as if it were a straight bridge.  You begin 
to walk on it.

khanjar9526@khanjar.title: Before A Decayed Building
khanjar9526@khanjar.description:
You are standing at a grass-covered yard.  Just to the west lies 
what may have been an inn of some kind years ago.  Now its roof and many 
of the other wooden parts are mostly gone, and the greyish walls break 
off so badly that you somewhat wonder how the building still stands.  An 
open doorway gives passage inside.  To the north lies an old pen.

khanjar9523@khanjar.title: A Jet-black Pond...
khanjar9523@khanjar.description:
Suddenly you are fallen down into jet-black and very cold water.
Bubbles raise to the surface and at the same moment you feel a touch
on your feet.  This feels ominous, as though there were something
housing the bloody pool.

khanjar9564@khanjar.title: An Ancient Crater
khanjar9564@khanjar.description:
You find yourself standing at a vast and deep pit, obviously an 
ancient crater with a diameter of 30 metres, at least.  The bottom is 
covered in brownish grass and there are several rough boulders around, 
most of them black.  Also you notice that the crater is full of small 
folk, everyone directing towards a structure of some kind further away 
to the east.

khanjar9527@khanjar.title: Inside An Old Pen
khanjar9527@khanjar.description:
The muddy ground here is covered in wooden fragments and old junk, 
nothing of interest.  To the north the forest gets thicker.

khanjar9569@khanjar.title: Descending The Steps
khanjar9569@khanjar.description: You start descending from the dais.

khanjar9552@khanjar.title: A Grassy Ditch
khanjar9552@khanjar.description:
You are standing on a grassy bottom of the ditch, seemingly trampled.  
Low bushes grow around.  The ditch leads west, while there is a grove to 
the east.

khanjar9520@khanjar.title: A Low Hillside
khanjar9520@khanjar.description:
This is a low, bush-growing hillside.  The path appears to be leading
toward what looks a small marshland down there.  For some reason it does 
not look very fascinating.

khanjar9509@khanjar.title: A Dusty Room
khanjar9509@khanjar.description:
The room has been furnished by a small elegant table, a strong 
bed, an old bookcase, and a chest of drawers.  Somehow you feel that
it won't be hired out so often, although it seems that no one has 
been here in a few weeks.  But no doubt, there is someone's property 
around...

khanjar9532@khanjar.title: A Weak Trail
khanjar9532@khanjar.description:
You step forward.  To the north is a small square, and to the south
there is a grove of somekind.  The trail itself leads to the west and east.

khanjar9508@khanjar.title: At The Top Floor
khanjar9508@khanjar.description:
This north- and south-directed corridor is where the local guest 
rooms are located at.  The walls are paneled in some fine wood, and 
there hang deep green tapestries with some white decorations on them.  
Torches cast soft light into the space.

khanjar9521@khanjar.title: The Marshland
khanjar9521@khanjar.description:
As you reach the marshland, the clouds of insects catch you 
in their unpleasant embrace, penetrating your very equipment.  You 
move on quickly, over the damp hummocks and over the small pools of 
black disgusting water, to escape those tiny winged beasts.  Further 
away to the north seems to be an another hillside, growing high trees.  
   Remainders of a bridge-like structure still lie here, leading
across the marsh.

khanjar9542@khanjar.title: At The Midst Of Some Edges
khanjar9542@khanjar.description:
You are walking between some edges.  Since most of them seem to be quite 
sharp, it is wise to be careful, this is not the day to get impaled.  To 
the north is what appears a brink.  Also, the mountainside above remains 
climbable.

khanjar9502@khanjar.title: The Yard Of The Tavern
khanjar9502@khanjar.description:
This is a large yard growing plenty of grass and a few high bushes
here and there.  The paving leads straight toward the tavern, but there
is also a faint trail to the west.  This could be a place to have fun,
at least some voices of singing are heard from inside the building.

khanjar9516@khanjar.title: A Path
khanjar9516@khanjar.description:
The path seems to descend toward the east where you can make out 
some sandy ground.

khanjar9522@khanjar.title: Stepping On Hammocks
khanjar9522@khanjar.description:
The most sturdiest hammocks here resist your weight easily, and 
thus you are able to move on.  Close to the east grows a large, somewhat
peculiar bush that covers your vision quite totally.

khanjar9519@khanjar.title: A Grassy Path
khanjar9519@khanjar.description:
A grassy but quite a wide path leads here.  According a few deep
grooves that are yet visible on it, this way was probably used much, a
long time ago. 
   Leaning against a greyish tree, there is a rottening, wooden sign.

khanjar9524@khanjar.title: The Marshland
khanjar9524@khanjar.description:
You are walking at the northern part of the marshland.  Just to 
the north is an another hillside, high and much more steeper than the 
one you just descended.  It grows some deep brown hay and tall birches.  
A faint trail climbs on it.

khanjar9561@khanjar.title: Under The Massive Roots
khanjar9561@khanjar.description:
Here the path goes very deep in the ground, almost as if it were 
an ancient trench.  Tremendous, gnarled roots from some brown and black
arches above.  The path leads both to the west and east.

khanjar9545@khanjar.title: On The Mountainside
khanjar9545@khanjar.description:
Climbing changes more and more difficult as you struggle on.  
It would take a long time to find a reasonable way to climb forward.  
And if one existed it would still be very arduous at all events.

khanjar9518@khanjar.title: An Intersection of Paths
khanjar9518@khanjar.description:
You are standing at a small square from where trails lead north, west, 
and east.  Since the foliage dominates your vision more or less, only the 
highest of Towers of Sundhaven can be seen farther to the west.

khanjar9534@khanjar.title: A Square of Mushrooms
khanjar9534@khanjar.description:
You are standing at a small square, surrounded by tall trees.  Dozens 
of deep brown mushrooms grow here, seemingly alluring the animals of the 
forest, for many of them appear munched.  The trail lies to the southeast.

khanjar9505@khanjar.title: The Lavatory
khanjar9505@khanjar.description:
The lavatory is quite cramped and the smell around exactly what it 
uses to be in places like this.  However the inside is very tidy, 
seemingly taken care often.  Anyway, you are ready to leave now...

khanjar9550@khanjar.title: On The Hill
khanjar9550@khanjar.description:
You are standing on a low and barren hill.  There are several 
footprints on it.  There is a small grove to the north.

khanjar9544@khanjar.title: Higher Up
khanjar9544@khanjar.description:
Conducted by a gentle wind you climb the mountainside and reach 
some space to rest on.  Taking a look at the sky you see a small eagle 
flying round the summit and vanishing into the canyons.  You can still 
continue to the south but it seems difficult to ascend the hillside any 
higher.

khanjar9541@khanjar.title: Before A Gigantic Boulder
khanjar9541@khanjar.description:
Wedged in at the ancient times, the massive boulder projects here
before you.  It is black all over and partly of some glasslike material.  
Some &+Cremnants&* lie under it.  The plateau extends to the west.

khanjar9560@khanjar.title: A Narrow Path
khanjar9560@khanjar.description:
You step on a narrow path, engraved deep in the ground.  Several 
stones make your walking quite difficult, and you are worried about 
your feet.  The foliages form a green and inpenetrable "wall" around 
the path which seems to descend to the east.

khanjar9574@khanjar.title: Climbing the Gorge
khanjar9574@khanjar.description:
Despite all better judgements, you claw your way along the side of the
walls.  Be aware though, one false move and you will fall to your death.

khanjar9510@khanjar.title: At The Top Floor
khanjar9510@khanjar.description:
You walk on the corridor.  A door to the west is ajar and you 
wonder if you heard some voices from behind it.

khanjar9540@khanjar.title: Climbing On The Mountainside
khanjar9540@khanjar.description:
You ascend a narrow split and arrive at a small plateau that 
continues both south and east.  Dark fungus appears to grow profuse
here.

khanjar9530@khanjar.title: The Top Of The Stairs
khanjar9530@khanjar.description:
You are standing at the second floor of these ruins which seem to 
swing every time you take a move.  There is no go to the north.  Once 
apparently so elegant passage has vanished, totally rottened, and 
collapsed away.

khanjar9567@khanjar.title: Before The Wooden Steps
khanjar9567@khanjar.description:
Just before you lie firm, wooden steps, ascending onto the dias.  
Simple, but elegant symbols have been encarved on them.

khanjar9528@khanjar.title: An Empty Vestibule
khanjar9528@khanjar.description:
You find yourself standing inside a dark vestibule, where the walls 
are covered in vast cobwebs and some strange smears.  The wind blows in 
from the holes of the walls, almost sounding as if there were a few small 
spirits howling their regret.  To the north is a door, blackened but still 
in existence.  Rather dangerous looking stairs lead upwards.

khanjar9515@khanjar.title: A Path
khanjar9515@khanjar.description:
As the path finds its way through the forest it sometimes becomes 
very narrow, wriggling by the side of some large stones.  Passing by 
a wagon of any kind would be impossible.  To the east grows dense 
thicket.

khanjar9539@khanjar.title: Walking On Stony Soil
khanjar9539@khanjar.description:
As you walk on, the mountainside begins to change much more steeper 
before you.  However it seems that you can advance easily enough.

khanjar9512@khanjar.title: At The Top Floor
khanjar9512@khanjar.description:
The corridor ends here, and you find yourself standing by a small
window.  Vast fields and forest are seen through it - everything looks
peaceful out there, despite a few alarming rumours about the Forces of
Evil gathering their power again.
   To the west stands a wooden door.

khanjar9517@khanjar.title: A Small Dell
khanjar9517@khanjar.description:
You descend onto a sandy dell where you notice some old marks of 
water, approximately flown here a few months ago.  The path continues to 
the east, climbing over great roots.

khanjar9562@khanjar.title: A Small Meadow
khanjar9562@khanjar.description:
You arrive at a small meadow that grows tall yellowish hay, swaying 
slowly in the wind.  The path leads towards the north, where you make out 
some high osiers.

khanjar9537@khanjar.title: A Lighter Forest
khanjar9537@khanjar.description:
You are approaching the edge of the forest from where a stony 
mountainside begins to ascend, very gentle at first.  Rippling of 
water can be heard from nearby.

khanjar9563@khanjar.title: On A Trail Through High Osiers
khanjar9563@khanjar.description:
Despite the thickness of these bushes you still detect the path and 
walk on it easily.  Now your trip begins to wind downwards, from where you 
can hear some voices.

khanjar9507@khanjar.title: A Smoky Drawing-Room
khanjar9507@khanjar.description:
You have arrived at a large drawing-room where quite an amount of 
tobacco smoke hovers about, forcing you to cough loudly.  Heavy chairs 
and tables can be seen all around.  The room is full of people, youngsters 
and elders, riches and poors, all from the different social classes.
   There is a wide collection of various hunting weapons on the western 
wall.  The room is warmed up by a massive fireplace.

khanjar9553@khanjar.title: Walking At The Ditch
khanjar9553@khanjar.description:
You walk on the bottom of the ditch.  As the bushes vanish in the 
south you can see a grassy hillside, on where a narrow path descends.  
The ditch leads west and east.

khanjar9557@khanjar.title: Descending The Hillside
khanjar9557@khanjar.description:
You start climbing down a small worn-out path on the hillside.  Despite 
the fresh footprints all around, the way doesn't appear very busy.

khanjar9535@khanjar.title: A Weak Trail
khanjar9535@khanjar.description:
You are walking on a narrow trail.  The trees are getting more 
apart slowly, and you hear birds singing here and there.  Way farther 
to the east raises a tremendous, grey figure, the mountainside of
Great Aesarthwe.

khanjar9500@khanjar.title: A Paved Path
khanjar9500@khanjar.description:
You are standing at the edge of the city.  From here, a short, 
paved path leads toward the east.  To the northeast is a large building, 
its yard lined by an old fence of stone.

khanjar9525@khanjar.title: A Steep Hillside
khanjar9525@khanjar.description:
You ascend the hillside, struggling between the trees and their 
twisted branches.  A figure of grey building begins to discern slowly 
to the northwest.

khanjar9506@khanjar.title: Inside The Tavern
khanjar9506@khanjar.description:
The walls here are paneled in some wood of various deep brown 
tints.  A large, wooden chandelier lits the room, making it very 
homely.  The furniture is dominated by a tall desk close to the north 
wall.  Behind it there stands a large, impressive &+Ccupboard&*.  To the 
west is a high, arched doorway, above which a huge bearhead has been
fastened, welcoming the customers in.
   Broad stairs lead up.

khanjar9573@khanjar.title: Climbing the Gorge
khanjar9573@khanjar.description:
Despite all better judgements, you claw your way along the side of the
walls.  Be aware though, one false move and you will fall to your death.

khanjar9511@khanjar.title: A Guest Room
khanjar9511@khanjar.description:
The air in this room is musty, and it smells of hard liquor.  On
the floor there lie a bundle of creased clothes and a couple of muddy
shoes.  As you step toward the window you notice that the floor there
is sticky and covered in thousands of tiny glass fragments all around.
   Obviously there has been a festival of some kind in the City at
last night.

khanjar9548@khanjar.title: Inside The Hollow Trunk
khanjar9548@khanjar.description:
As you crawl through a small hole you notice that the huge tree is 
completely hollow, and enables you to move about.  Some kind of ladder 
leads down from here.

khanjar9501@khanjar.title: Before A Small Gate
khanjar9501@khanjar.description:
The paving turns toward the north, toward the wooden gate of 
the fence.  A sign has been fastened on the gate, reading "Barumafir's
Tavern".  A brown path leads to the east, toward light forest.

khanjar9572@khanjar.title: Climbing the Gorge
khanjar9572@khanjar.description:
Despite all better judgements, you claw your way along the side of the
walls.  Be aware though, one false move and you will fall to your death.

khanjar9529@khanjar.title: A Chaotic Room
khanjar9529@khanjar.description:
The room is in chaotic order.  Parts of the upper floor have fallen 
down here, and the former furniture is now more or less buried under them.
At the corners there lie several rottening books, bedraggled tapestries,
and broken vessels.  Besides, the room appears partially burned.

khanjar9551@khanjar.title: A Small Grove
khanjar9551@khanjar.description:
You are standing at a peaceful grove, surrounded by those 
evergrowing trees and various flowers which all look so beautiful, 
but also somewhat sad.  
   There is a large ant hill, and as a contrast to the grove it 
nearly swarms life.  A faint track leads to the north, and to the
west there lies a ditch.

khanjar9576@khanjar.title: Climbing the Gorge
khanjar9576@khanjar.description:
Despite all better judgements, you claw your way along the side of the
walls.  Be aware though, one false move and you will fall to your death.

khanjar9513@khanjar.title: A Tidy Room
khanjar9513@khanjar.description:
The room is in extremely good order.  Every particle of dust or dirt
of any kind appear to be wiped out.  Apparently there is a possible tenant
coming soon.

khanjar9503@khanjar.title: On The Lawn
khanjar9503@khanjar.description:
You step on the lawn.  An old, large tree lines the track, and its 
foliage covers the yard in massive shadows.  The corner of the tavern is
close to the west.

khanjar9554@khanjar.title: A Grassy Ditch
khanjar9554@khanjar.description:
You are standing on the bottom of a small and grassy ditch.  There 
is some thicket growing around.  The ditch leads to the east.

khanjar9570@khanjar.title: Descending The Steps
khanjar9570@khanjar.description: You start descending from the dais.

khanjar9556@khanjar.title: The Brink Of The Grassy Hillside
khanjar9556@khanjar.description:
You are standing on the brink of the grassy hillside that begins 
to descend gently.  Below there lies what appears very dense forest.
To the north is a ditch.

khanjar9531@khanjar.title: A Weak Trail
khanjar9531@khanjar.description:
The forest appears thicker now.  Massive trees tower around, making 
you feel yourself tiny and pitiful compared to those old giants.  The trail
here is quite narrow.

khanjar9543@khanjar.title: The Brink Of A Gorge
khanjar9543@khanjar.description:
You are standing on the brink of a deep, deep gorge.  Its walls are 
very smooth and rush straight down, where nothing but a jet-black 
emptiness can be seen.

khanjar9504@khanjar.title: By The Side Of The Tavern
khanjar9504@khanjar.description:
You are standing close to the western fence of the yard.  The city 
can be seen further to the west - masses of people and clamour.  To the 
is a small, wooden, cell-like building, obviously a lavatory.

khanjar9536@khanjar.title: A Weak Trail
khanjar9536@khanjar.description:
The forest is clearly more lighter now, and you sense gentle sunshine 
on your cheeks.  The trail leads east toward the mountain, and west, into 
the deeper forest.

khanjar9565@khanjar.title: At The Crater
khanjar9565@khanjar.description:
With the brownies you start approaching the structure as well.
It looks like a wooden dais, on where a couple of beings are sitting, 
deep in their discussion.  Behind them there stands what could be a 
totem or a statue of some kind.  Yet you do not know what this all is 
about, but no doubt this place must be of great importance and sanctity 
for these people.

khanjar9559@khanjar.title: Walking On The Trunk
khanjar9559@khanjar.description:
You move forward, keeping your balance quite easily since the trunk 
is so broad.  It seems that many smaller trees remained under when this 
giant overturned years ago.
   Now, there lies the rhizome.  The roots appear to give passage to 
the south.

khanjar9547@khanjar.title: Under A Brown Dome
khanjar9547@khanjar.description:
You are standing inside a brownish chamber, under some massive 
roots, from which various fibres with soil still hang down.  There 
are small footprints on the ground.  While an improvised ladder leads 
up, there is a small, wooden door the east.

khanjar9568@khanjar.title: The Ceremony Plateau
khanjar9568@khanjar.description:
The dais has been grinded very smooth.  Four green pictures cover 
its surface, representing fine trees.  Each picture points to the sepa-
rate cardinal direction.  In the middle of the dais stands a tall, wooden 
&+Cstatue&*, resembling an impressive woman, clad in clothes made of large 
leaves and garments.
   The brownies assemble to the foot of the dais and you feel the
atmosphere running high.

khanjar9571@khanjar.title: Gorge
khanjar9571@khanjar.description:
There is a faint smell of ozone in the air.  You are in a deep gorge below
the mountain peaks, where you find some relief from the constant wind.  There
are some markings in the rocks, and some of them appear to have melted at some
point in the near past.  Apparently lightning storms are a common occurance
here.  There is a path that snakes between the rocks and boulders, difficult
and treacherous but passable.

khanjar9555@khanjar.title: Through The Bushes
khanjar9555@khanjar.description:
You are struggling at a thicket, disturbed by several multicolorous 
spiders and gadflies.  Most of these bushes are unusually tough, lashing 
your face with an unpleasant force.  There is a small ditch to the south.

khanjar9575@khanjar.title: Climbing the Gorge
khanjar9575@khanjar.description:
Despite all better judgements, you claw your way along the side of the
walls.  Be aware though, one false move and you will fall to your death.

khanjar9533@khanjar.title: A Weak Trail
khanjar9533@khanjar.description:
You have arrived at a bend.  From here the trail turns to the north, 
leading through the dark green arch of the gigantic trees.  To the south
lies a small grove.

mob9508_3@khanjar.name: mob9508_3
mob9508_3@khanjar.examine:
What a jolly being.  His face is reddish and he looks very kind. 
The clothes he wears are of cheerfully woven and brown leather, some 
of them simply patterned.  As he were ascertaining something, he utters 
odd words and beckons his companier.
mob9508_3@khanjar.description: A small, long-bearded man is standing here.

Not too enviable.
mob9505@khanjar.description: A pale man is lying on the bed, moaning faintly.

mob9501_1@khanjar.description: A herdsman sits here, concentrating on his beer.

mob9504@khanjar.examine:
Barumafir is a middle-aged, shortlike man with a bad sciatica. 
But he does well with his tavern.
mob9504@khanjar.description: Barumafir, the keeper of this tavern is standing here.

mob9506_1@khanjar.examine:

With a sick glow in his eyes he attacks you, intending to rob every-
thing you possess.
mob9506_1@khanjar.description: A fierce ragamuffin rushes toward you from the shadows.

as a dwarf he looks very robust, and a huge rucksack and a bunch 
of utilities, such as hammers and dark chisels, seem to be carried
as though they weighted nothing.
mob9503@khanjar.description: A taciturn dwarf is standing here, fingering his beard.

mob9514@khanjar.examine:
She is tall and well-proportioned.  The dark hair descends on the 
light brown skin, making no curls.  Her big eyes radiate wisdom and 
pleasant heat, making it difficult to leave this fabulous being.  
She appears to enjoy high esteem amidst the small folk of this forest.
mob9514@khanjar.description: A beautiful centaur rests on the dais.

mob9513@khanjar.examine:

before, although being a bit shorter.  But somehow you feel their 
personality might be entirely unlike, and include sides which are 
dark and strange.
mob9513@khanjar.description: A hobgoblin stands here, grinning at you broadly.

mob9510@khanjar.name: mob9510
mob9510@khanjar.examine:
These strange monsters are slimy and their skin is covered in the 
shaking rings of meat and vesicles.  They have several ugly heads with 
an eye standing on the each.  The land of Gwyte is where they come from. 
It is rumouded that they serve the Evil and therefore were sent around 
as messengers of horror.
mob9510@khanjar.description: A greenish creature with many tentacles rises from the pond!

that short sword on her side, she is something more than just a 
normal housewife.
